<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 — The Fullz Shop</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { background: #0a0a0b; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .container { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; }
    .code { font-size: 6rem; font-weight: 900; color: #ff0040; text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(255,0,64,0.3); }
    h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; color: #fff; }
    p { color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    a { color: #00ff41; text-decoration: none; padding: 0.8rem 2rem; border: 1px solid #00ff41; border-radius: 8px; transition: all 0.3s; }
    a:hover { background: #00ff41; color: #000; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="code">404</div>
    <h1>Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>The page you're looking for doesn't exist or has been moved.</p>
    <a href="/">← Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
